<br>
There were a few touchy moments, like me getting charmed and almost beating Kelwan to death, but all in all, a successful hunt.  The spoils were nothing to write home about, that short way into the zone, but I got almost 2 bubbles of XP.  Even Yanamila, at 14th level, got a bubble of XP.  As I was leaving, I asked her, &quot;Did you ever think you'd have a good time in Mistmoore at 14th?&quot;  <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->   <br>
<br>
I have a couple personal awards to give out, based partly on things in guildchat:<br>
Best stupid Paladin trick goes to Varigon, as usual, for leaping back into battle naked (I think he may have picked up his sword) while waiting for a rez.<br>
Best use of a non-tradeskill goes to Askyn, for feigning death, thereby avoiding getting wiped out with the rest of his group.<br>
<br>
Thank you all for making this such an enjoyable hunt for me. <p><FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Verdana,Arial"><B>Finrael Briteside</B><BR>
