 I am sorry there so many deaths, but was very glad I could help Balamur doing his rezs buy giving him every point of mana I could regen ... <br>
<br>
 I recommend for the next hunt:<br>
<br>
 1) Upper Guk ... some good drops not too far in. Deceant progression of difficulty. Lowers could stay toward the front/middle part of the zone ..highers could go to the middle/rear of the zone. Everything here is a 18 min respawn.<br>
<br>
 2) Dalnir? I think a good group of mid to upper 20's could do the 2nd floor fairly easy ... just need a enchanter to help break it up at first .. every thing there is a 12 minute respawn. The Imp room on the 2nd floor is very nice .. 3 or 4 spawn spots ... just go in invis .. have the enchanter mezz .. than kill 1, wait 3mins kill next .. etc.   nice way of breaking the room .. leaves lots of time for pulls of the lumpy goos ... Oh - one point ... DONT ATTACK the NIBBLERS that dont attack you FIRST!!! This is essential, the non agro keep the place sane! and keep the people from being swamped by a bunch of stuff all at once.<br>
<br>
